subpod.plaintext: Actress and pop singer-songwriter who gained notable fame for her role on the Disney Channel's sitcom and franchise Hannah Montana, which established her as a teen idol Performed in concert as both herself and as character Hannah Montana on the Best of Both Worlds Tour Began presenting a more adult image with her 2009 album release Recorded the accompanying movie soundtracks for Hannah Montana and Hannah Montana 2/Meet Miley Cyrus
